# MainActivity Learning Topics

## High-Level Categories
1. Android Application Architecture
2. Jetpack Compose UI
3. Navigation
4. State Management
5. Dependency Injection
6. Theme Management

## Android/Kotlin Concepts Used

### Jetpack Compose
1. Core Components
   - ComponentActivity
   - Composable functions
   - Material3 theming
   - State management

2. UI Elements
   - Navigation
   - Theme customization
   - Status bar handling

### Architecture Components
1. ViewModel
   - ViewModelFactory
   - State handling
   - Dependency injection

2. Navigation
   - NavController
   - Route management
   - Deep linking

### State Management
1. Compose State
   - collectAsState
   - remember
   - mutableStateOf

2. Coroutines
   - LaunchedEffect
   - StateFlow

### Material Design
1. Theme Components
   - MaterialTheme
   - Color schemes
   - Dark mode

## Suggested Study Order

1. Basic Concepts
   - Activity Lifecycle
   - Compose Basics
   - Material Design

2. State Management
   - StateFlow
   - Compose State
   - ViewModel Integration

3. Navigation
   - NavController
   - Route Management
   - Arguments

4. Architecture
   - Dependency Injection
   - ViewModel Pattern
   - Repository Pattern

5. Advanced Topics
   - Deep Linking
   - State Restoration
   - UI Testing

## Key Technologies
- Jetpack Compose
- Material3
- Navigation Component
- ViewModel
- StateFlow
- SystemUiController

